  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>MINIGAMES AND FLYING?</strong></h2><br>In FAILURE TO LAUNCH, complete difficult minigames while also SIMULTANEOUSLY piloting a spaceship through an endless runner of obstacles. Danger is everywhere commander!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641590/extras/19cb984fa00212823f6c219f723f1806.poster.avif?t=1702007992\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641590/extras/19cb984fa00212823f6c219f723f1806.webm?t=1702007992\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641590/extras/19cb984fa00212823f6c219f723f1806.mp4?t=1702007992\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FAILURE IS AN OPTION</strong></h2><br>Fail a minigame or hit an obstacle, and your ship will meet a FIERY EXPLOSION. Are you skilled enough to drive and finish minigames AT THE SAME TIME? This game will put you to the multi tasking test! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641590/extras/ea140cc4643426936167b71f8c26bee4.poster.avif?t=1702007992\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641590/extras/ea140cc4643426936167b71f8c26bee4.webm?t=1702007992\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641590/extras/ea140cc4643426936167b71f8c26bee4.mp4?t=1702007992\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BONUS FEATURES APLENTY</strong></h2><br>With weekly Leaderboard seasons, an Unlock Tree, Achievements, and over 30 whacky unlockable ships, backgrounds and ship trails, there are tons of progression to keep you striving for more. Shoot for the stars on our online Leaderboard and prove if you have what it takes!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641590/extras/0a7fbd7beeae3b6e2e4cb017c92dbc1c.poster.avif?t=1702007992\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641590/extras/0a7fbd7beeae3b6e2e4cb017c92dbc1c.webm?t=1702007992\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641590/extras/0a7fbd7beeae3b6e2e4cb017c92dbc1c.mp4?t=1702007992\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<br><br>",
